Humans can justify just about anything. It’s what we’re good at. It keeps us sane and makes us crazy.




The price we pay for sentience, I guess. Lower animals do not
understand therefore do not comprehend therefore needn’t make sense of
the world. But on the other hand, we’re not scared of vacuums.




